## Why Look for Rockerbox Alternatives?

Rockerbox is excellent for multi-channel brands—podcast tracking, TV measurement, MMM included. But it's not for everyone. (Full disclosure: mbuzz is one of the alternatives we cover. If you're investing heavily in podcasts, TV, or direct mail, Rockerbox's offline channel tracking is genuinely best-in-class—we'll help you decide what fits.)

**Common reasons to explore alternatives:**

| Limitation | Impact |
|------------|--------|
| **Strategic, not tactical** | Less suited for daily media buying optimization |
| **Limited model flexibility** | Fewer attribution models, no custom logic |
| **Overkill for digital-only** | Podcast/TV features wasted if you don't use them |
| **Complexity** | CMO-level tool, steep for smaller teams |
| **Proxy method accuracy** | Podcast/TV measurement has inherent limitations |

If any of these resonate, here are your best options.

