### What mbuzz Offers

**Server-side tracking that captures the full journey.** While Rockerbox uses client-side tracking plus proxy methods for podcasts/TV, mbuzz tracks on your backend—no ad blockers, no missing digital touchpoints. 95%+ event capture vs the 70% typical of client-side tools.

**8 attribution models with side-by-side comparison.** Compare First Touch, Last Touch, Linear, Time Decay, U-Shaped, W-Shaped, plus data-driven Markov Chain and Shapley Value. See how different models credit your channel mix—Rockerbox's MMM gives aggregate insight; mbuzz shows touchpoint-level detail.

