**Custom attribution rules for complex funnels.** Define your own logic in minutes:

```ruby
# Multi-channel: Give awareness channels first-touch credit
model "awareness_to_conversion" do
  if position == :first && channel.in?(["podcast", "tv", "influencer"])
    weight 0.40
  elsif position == :last && channel.in?(["paid_search", "retargeting"])
    weight 0.35
  else
    weight :linear
  end
end
```

**LTV attribution that Rockerbox lacks.** Track every recurring payment back to original acquisition source. That podcast sponsor might look expensive on first purchase but deliver 3x LTV—mbuzz shows the full story.

